Connect Your Application to Large Language Models with Models API (Beta)

Models API enhances your application with large language models (LLMs) from Salesforce partners. You can use Models API for different scenarios that benefit from generative AI.

Where: This change applies to Lightning Experience in Enterprise, Performance, and Unlimited editions with an Einstein for Sales, Einstein for Platform, or Einstein for Service add-on.

NOTE This feature is a Beta Service. Any use of the Beta Service is subject to the applicable Beta Services Terms provided at Agreements and Terms.

When: Models API (Beta) feature is available starting in July 2024.

Who: This feature is available to Salesforce customers with Data Cloud and Einstein permission sets.

How: Developers can access Models API with REST or Apex.
